{"tid":1972923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍關島B-52H核戰略轟炸機秀「大象漫步」","createTime":"2020-04-14T23:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T18:11:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb97c81c4cd5a9e6e8016d5ea2504c99c3ee904","tid":1972923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:23:18.000Z","msg":"美軍關島B-52H核戰略轟炸機秀「大象漫步」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taiwandaily.net/%e7%be%8e%e8%bb%8d%e9%97%9c%e5%b3%b6b-52h%e6%a0%b8%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e8%bd%9f%e7%82%b8%e6%a9%9f%e7%a7%80%e3%80%8c%e5%a4%a7%e8%b1%a1%e6%bc%ab%e6%ad%a5%e3%80%8d/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwandaily.net%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%25bb%258d%25e9%2597%259c%25e5%25b3%25b6b-52h%25e6%25a0%25b8%25e6%2588%25b0%25e7%2595%25a5%25e8%25bd%259f%25e7%2582%25b8%25e6%25a9%259f%25e7%25a7%2580%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e8%25b1%25a1%25e6%25bc%25ab%25e6%25ad%25a5%25e3%2580%258d%2F&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=14051592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwandaily.net/%e7%be%8e%e8%bb%8d%e9%97%9c%e5%b3%b6b-52h%e6%a0%b8%e6%88%b0%e7%95%a5%e8%bd%9f%e7%82%b8%e6%a9%9f%e7%a7%80%e3%80%8c%e5%a4%a7%e8%b1%a1%e6%bc%ab%e6%ad%a5%e3%80%8d/</a><br />\n<br />\n「羅斯福號」在內的美軍4艘核動力航空母艦，因艦內爆發新型冠狀病毒（COVID-19，下稱武漢肺炎）疫情，被迫返港隔離，影響印太地區部署，中國解放軍航艦「遼寧號」趁隙通過我國東部海域挑釁，不過美軍也在關島進行包含5架B-52H戰略轟炸機的「大象漫步」，展現其在印太地區仍有足夠戰力。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n據航空新聞網站《The Aviationist》報導，關島的美軍安德森空軍基地（Andersen Air Force Base）在當地時間13日進行「大象漫步」（Elephant Walk）的戰力展示，大批戰機首尾相連在跑道上緩緩前進，以便於在最短時間內起飛最多戰機，考驗飛行員的應變與操控能力，是展現空軍實力的方法之一。<br />\n<br />\n5架具備核打擊能力的B-52H戰略轟炸機、6架KC-135大型加油機，空軍RQ-4「全球鷹」無人機、海軍MQ-4C「海神」無人偵察機，以及海軍MH-60S「海鷹」直升機在關島跑道排成縱隊，場面相當震撼</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，本次兵力展示的意圖很明顯，展現美軍太平洋空軍第36聯隊的戰備能力和隨時可投入作戰的能力，表明可確保整個印度太平洋地區的穩定。自由時報0414"},{"pid":"f8be6746a9a7b7fd82907ddbfaeacf230ac0d4b6","tid":1972923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T23:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ef0729db92cfc70a3fe2f831e53be440df2846","tid":1972923,"uid":93649,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:05:34.000Z","msg":"你地打啦 我好悶呀"},{"pid":"a8535e9e84a49713b3e31afec9aac7f4ef8d6194","tid":1972923,"uid":179114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:10:21.000Z","msg":"我好似聽到星戰既音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f1c1a455e9ef365124ac567e8b3e59b18072cc","tid":1972923,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:12:12.000Z","msg":"協議左入買油嘛，用唔晒咪整下演集"},{"pid":"e634e552da29fbc5ec3fe6174d466851bc9ec2c3","tid":1972923,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f1b229a44e7f6cca8768b7e48ed5a7f565f2ff","tid":1972923,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T00:52:24.000Z","msg":"邵家臻議員為還押手足發起「和你做筆友」計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1972952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1972952</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f04c84cb5614cd868f3afce2059e9912bb16cc65","tid":1972923,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T01:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e446853ee07d0a0452efe03395d81e50dff7a","tid":1972923,"uid":3776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T03:05:14.000Z","msg":"轟佢老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34a23901f1347dba68363c0fc48f804338a88a9","tid":1972923,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T03:10:03.000Z","msg":"咁舊既機 支那唔係淆底呀"},{"pid":